Name: MythTV-Database reconfigure required
Priority: High
Terminal: False
DontShowAfterReboot: True
Description: The mythtv-database was upgraded or installed, but couldn't contact
 Your mysql server.  Verify that you provided the correct information and that
 the server is running, and re-run sudo dpkg-reconfigure mythtv-database.
 If you were dist-upgrading, this is normal as mysql-server is stopped for the
 upgrade.
